summary: Tiny Titus ( Dutch Citizen) is an Ayurveda Doctor with work experience in India, United Kingdom, and the Netherlands. She  successfully completed Bachelor in Ayurvedic Medicine and Surgery (B.A.M.S) from  the University of Kerala which is a full time course that prepares students to become a registered Ayurveda Doctor in Kerala.B.A.M.S. Graduates can work as Ayurveda Doctors in India.B.A.M.S. is a full time course with a duration of 6 years which includes 4.5 years of study and 1year internship. She successfully completed a one-year compulsory internship in government Ayurveda hospitals in Kerala. Tiny Titus also successfully completed Netherlands Course on Global Health and Tropical Medicine from KIT Royal Tropical Institute Amsterdam, Netherlands(Full Time).She have successfully completed a course on Rebuilding disrupted health systems, GIS, Monitoring and evaluation in a dynamic environment from KIT Royal Tropical Institute Amsterdam. She is living in Netherlands for 7 years.
